Create new project:
petalinux-create --type project --template zynq

Configure:
petalinux-config
petalinux-config -c kernel
petalinux-config -c rootfs

Create C application:
petalinux-create -t apps --template c --name <name>
petalinux-build -c <name>
petalinux-config -c rootfs

Useful links:
https://xilinx-wiki.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/A/pages/18842475/PetaLinux+Yocto+Tips


